episodes.title: 🎙️ How Gary Coxe Deprogrammed 45 Years of Cult Conditioning & Took His Life Back
episodes.description:
🎙️ How Gary Coxe Deprogrammed 45 Years of Cult Conditioning & Took His Life Back

Gary Coxe is a renowned business and life strategist, bestselling author, and transformational speaker whose journey from tragedy to triumph has inspired millions.

Born and raised in Kingston, Jamaica, Gary launched his entrepreneurial journey early—owning a fine jewelry store and earning over $100K a year by age 17. But life took a dark turn. After the murder of his father and the loss of his business, Gary hit rock bottom.

What followed was a powerful story of reinvention. Gary became his own “doctor and patient,” developing mindset strategies that helped him escape 45 years of cult programming and take control of his life.

His breakthrough methods have been featured on The View, Inside Edition, and The Doctors. Today, he helps people shatter mental limits, overcome trauma, and build lives of purpose and peak performance.

🎧 In this episode, we dive deep into Gary’s story—and how you can use his strategies to transform your own life.
